CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 28, 1962, pg. 31 reads:"Cited By Iron City - Iron City Lodge 17, IBPOE of W, honored its Exalted Ruler, Louis J. McTurner, at a testimonial banquet on April 22, at the Iron City Home on Centre Ave. Standing, left to right: R. Charles Wright, toastmaster; seated: Joseph W. Givens, DDGE; Fred Montgomery; Oscar Price, PGER; Robert (Pappy) Williams, magistrate; Jouis J. McTurner (honoree), Ed Myles, William L. Thomas, Roy Waker and Atty. Wendell Freeland. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: R. Charles Wright standing on left, and seated: Joseph W. Givens, Fred Montgomery, Oscar Price, Robert "Pappy" Williams, Jouis J. McTurner, honoree, shaking hands with unknown man; Ed Myles, William L. Thomas, Roy Waker, and Wendell Freeland, gathered at banquet table in Iron City Elks Lodge 17 for testimonial banquet
